    <h2>Your face.<br>Their fantasy.</h2>
    <p>Real portraits. AI-generated fantasy. These are actual passport pages generated by the PrismaLive system — Ritsu in Japan, Aaron in France. Every visitor receives their own.</p>
  </div>
