<!-- VISITOR JOURNEY -->
<section class="section section-dark" id="journey">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="kicker">Visitor Journey</span>
    <h2>Start here.<br>Exit through<br>the gift shop.</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="journey-grid">
    <div class="journey-step">
      <span class="step-num">01 — START HERE</span>
      <span class="step-icon">📸</span>
      <h3>Passport Registration</h3>
      <p>A Media Lab Midwest photographer greets visitors and invites them to register. Warm, playful atmosphere — passport control reimagined as a party.</p>
      <p>Visitor taps NFC tag. Photographer takes portrait. Image loads into digital passport on visitor's phone.</p>
      <span class="step-note">No app · No login · Bring your phone</span>
    </div>
    <div class="journey-step">
      <span class="step-num">02</span>
      <span class="step-icon">🗺️</span>
      <h3>Eight Country Stations</h3>
      <p>Visitor tours eight stations at their own pace: Japan, India, France, Kenya, Saudi Arabia, Colombia, China, USA.</p>
      <p>Each station is a physical billboard card with the corporate PAC sponsor logo and an embedded NFC tag.</p>
      <span class="step-note">Self-guided · Any order · 20–30 min total</span>
    </div>
    <div class="journey-step">
      <span class="step-num">03</span>
      <span class="step-icon">📲</span>
      <h3>Tap, Watch, Receive</h3>
      <p>Visitor taps the NFC tag embedded in the sponsor card. Corporate sponsor ad plays immediately — 10–15 seconds of branded content.</p>
      <p>While the ad plays, PrismaLive AI composites the visitor into that country's cinematic backdrop.</p>
      <span class="step-note">The ad is the entry point</span>
      <span class="sponsored-tag">Sponsored Content</span>
    </div>
    <div class="journey-step">
      <span class="step-num">04 — VIEW RESULTS</span>
      <span class="step-icon">🖥️</span>
      <h3>Central Screen — Live Gallery</h3>
      <p>Every generated image displays in real time on a large central screen, visible beyond the installation walls.</p>
      <p>The piece draws in new visitors through the spectacle of others being transformed.</p>
      <span class="step-note">Powered by PrismaLive · medialabmidwest.com</span>
    </div>
    <div class="journey-step">
      <span class="step-num">05</span>
      <span class="step-icon">🌐</span>
      <h3>Completion — Global Citizen</h3>
      <p>After all eight stations: congratulations screen. "You are now a Global Citizen."</p>
      <p>Then the reveal: every country was a stereotype built for them, every image AI-generated, every stamp paid for by a corporation purchasing its own political dominance.</p>
      <span class="step-note">opensecrets.org — look up your representative's donors</span>
    </div>
    <div class="journey-step">
      <span class="step-num">06 — EXIT HERE</span>
      <span class="step-icon">🏪</span>
      <h3>The Vending Machine</h3>
      <p>A vending machine of local products, encouraging visitors to question corporate sponsorships and support local businesses.</p>
      <p>Real products. Local makers. Real money. No screens. The only honest object in the room.</p>
      <span class="step-note">The world tour was sponsored. Your neighborhood is sponsor-free.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

